{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/album-terakhir-jonghyun-dirilis-banyak-pesan-tersirat-di-dalamnya/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Album Terakhir Jonghyun Dirilis, Banyak Pesan Tersirat di Dalamnya","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kabar kepergian Jonghyun salah satu anggota dari K-pop SHINee tanggal 18 Desember silam menggemparkan penggemar  Kpop di seluruh dunia. Bahkan, sampai sekarang pun berita duka tersebut masih membayangi para penggemarnya. Bahkan di Indonesia pun heboh berita seorang Shawol yang nekat bunuh diri untuk menyusul kepergian idola tercintanya. Sampai saat ini, sosok bertalenta ini masih dirindukan oleh banyak orang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42169\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42169\" data-attachment-id=\"42169\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/album-terakhir-jonghyun-dirilis-banyak-pesan-tersirat-di-dalamnya/attachment/1-2-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-2-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : cnn.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : cnn.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-2-3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-2-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42169\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-2-3.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : cnn.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-2-3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-2-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42169\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : cnn.com)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebulan setelah kepergiannya, Jonghyun masih memberikan kontribusi di dunia <em>entertainment. </em>Pasalnya sebelum kepergian Jonghyun, ia sudah menyelesaikan rekaman album terbarunya serta melakukan pemotretan <em>photobook.</em> Dikabarkan bahwa sehari sebelum bunuh diri, dirinya pun sempat melakukan syuting untuk <em>music video</em> single terbarunya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42170\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42170\" data-attachment-id=\"42170\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/album-terakhir-jonghyun-dirilis-banyak-pesan-tersirat-di-dalamnya/attachment/2-2-31/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: SM Town Entertainment)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: SM Town Entertainment)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42170\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-4.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: SM Town Entertainment)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-2-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42170\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: SM Town Entertainment)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tanggal 23 Januari kemarin, album terakhirnya yang berjudul “POET | ARTIST” telah dirilis secara <em>online</em>. Menyusul album fisiknya pada tanggal 24 Januari. Hingga saat ini, album terakhirnya tersebut berhasil menduduki peringkat pertama di iTunes berbagai negara, seperti Jepang, Denmark, Rusia, Turki, Thailand, Hongkong, Yunani, Firlandia, Malaysia, Peru, Singapura, dan negara lainnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42171\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42171\" data-attachment-id=\"42171\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/album-terakhir-jonghyun-dirilis-banyak-pesan-tersirat-di-dalamnya/attachment/3-2-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-2-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source: youtube.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-2-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-2-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42171\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-2-4.jpg\" alt=\"(Source: youtube.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-2-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-2-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42171\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Album POET | ARTIST berisikan 11 lagu, yaitu <em>Shinin, Only One You Need, #Hashtag, Grease, Take The Dive, Sightseeing, Rewind, Just for a day, I’m So Curious, Sentimental, dan Before Our Spring</em>. Beberapa lagu juga sempat dinyanyikan oleh mendiang Jonghyun dalam konser terakhirnya yang digelar pada bulan Desember 2017.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ada beberapa lagu yang diduga memiliki makna terselubung didalamnya, seperti <em>Only One You Need. </em>Lagu ini memiliki pesan kepada pendengar untuk tidak bersedih dan sakit karena kehilangan orang yang dicintai. Menurut penulis, Jonghyun ingin berpesan kepada penggemarnya untuk tidak merasa sedih dan sakit atas kepergiannya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42172\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42172\" data-attachment-id=\"42172\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/album-terakhir-jonghyun-dirilis-banyak-pesan-tersirat-di-dalamnya/attachment/4-2-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-2-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : aminoapps.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : aminoapps.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-2-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-2-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42172\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-2-4.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : aminoapps.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-2-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-2-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42172\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : aminoapps.com)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ada juga lagu #Hashtag, netizen menafsirkan bahwa lagu tersebut memiliki makna didalamnya. Sesuai perkataan Jonghyun pada konser terakhirnya, lagu ini ditulis karena inspirasi dari tanda hashtag (#) yang menyerupai pola dalam makanan wafel. Dalam Bahasa Korea, waffle (wa-pul) terdengar mirip dengan (ak-pul) yang berarti komentar jahat dan rumor tak berdasar.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jadi, waffle secara tersirat (penyebutan dalam bahasa korea) berarti menulis atau berbicara sesuatu yang panjang tanpa arti Mungkin maksud Jonghyun adalah, jika kita membenci seorang idola, sepatutnya jangan memberi komentar yang tidak benar untuk menjatuhkannya. Sebelum berkomentar, sebaiknya harus dipikirkan secara matang dan sesuai fakta. Karena, bagaimana pun mulut-mu adalah harimau-mu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42174\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42174\" data-attachment-id=\"42174\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/album-terakhir-jonghyun-dirilis-banyak-pesan-tersirat-di-dalamnya/attachment/6-2-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-2-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Source : allkpop.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Source : allkpop.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-2-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-2-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42174\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-2-4.jpg\" alt=\"(Source : allkpop.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-2-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/6-2-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42174\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Source : allkpop.com)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SMTown juga mengklaim bahwa keuntungan yang didapatkan dari hasil penjualan album tersebut, sepenuhnya akan diserahkan kepada Ibu Jonghyun dan digunakan untuk membantu membangun yayasan yang tengah kesulitan.</p>\n<p>Wah, bro sis udah dengar lagunya belum? Jika belum, yuk simak MV terakhir Jonghyun berikut ini.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/J41qe-TM1DY\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"ea8f8ebe-feec-5ede-ada6-17e7c051e7a4"}}}